column5: Then off to The Chapleau game preserve, Abbey lake with outpostcamps.com. Cant wait, we fished it last year and caught so many walleye it was almost stupid lol. So pumped!

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JlwdZfH7j1I Heres a fun self video last year up there, mid day, 2 walleye in a pass over spot, and some good ribbing of buddy that was snagged at end lol. Please excuse the amateur videoing lol.
